{
  "stem": "22660.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once she came, we were able to get a better apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she then cooked and baked for us, and cooked and baked for the people that we rented the rooms to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father still did this and that and my mother did what I told you what-- ill people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those years-- but for us, it was, again, not so terrible, because we had a house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had my mother and father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember I had-- took some dancing lessons and went to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for us, it really-- we were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very lucky that we got out on that last boat, because anything after, you know the story.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who were your friends at the time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Montevideo?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you see, a lot of people from all over Germany ended up in Montevideo, so we started immediately-- my father, who started [GERMAN], a German-Jewish synagogue.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother started the chapter of WIZO, Women's International Zionist Organization.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were friends with all the people that came from other places from Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And only after a while did we-- through school and through other ways, did we become friendly with people who were really born in Uruguay.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it took quite a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The German-Jewish community, there were many Jewish communities in Montevideo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was the German Jewish community, the Polish Jewish community, the Sephardic Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And each one had their own synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In our synagogue, they only spoke German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Uruguayans were very good to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents loved living in Montevideo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Uruguayans were very good to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- the anti-Semitism that people hear about existed in Argentina, but did not exist in Uruguay-- did not exist in Uruguay.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
